-- Manila Water’s First-Half Profit Rises 11% to 2.91 Billion Pesos
-- B y   I a n   S a y s o n
-- 2013-08-08T07:59:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-08-08/manila-water-s-first-half-profit-rises-11-to-2-91-billion-pesos.html
Manila Water Co.’s net income
increased 11 percent to 2.91 billion pesos ($67 million) from
2.63 billion pesos a year earlier, it said in filing with the
Philippine Stock Exchange.  Six-month sales rose 6 percent to 7.63 billion pesos from
7.19 billion pesos, the utility said. Costs of services and
operating expenses fell 2 percent to 2.1 billion pesos while its
share in income of associates more than doubled to 119 million
pesos, the filing show.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ian Sayson in Manila at 
